snippet.title: Grand Prix Circuit (Commodore 64)
snippet.description: Grand Prix Circuit, racing Monaco (badly). I cut the loading times to fit the video under 10 minutes. The loading times are not that long actually and there's a cool loading bar which I don't remember seeing in another C64 game.
